headline: Wells Fargo Reworks 2026 Staples Outlook, Cuts Church & Dwight (CHD) Target
summary: Church & Dwight Co., Inc. (NYSE:CHD) is included among the 13 Best Consumer Staples Dividend Stocks to Invest in Now.
